	systems.  From Fredrik Lingvall <Fredrik.Lingvall@signal.uu.se>.

	* mkoctfile.in: Allow -Wx,option style options to be passed to the
	compiler.  From Al Niessner <Al.Niessner@jpl.nasa.gov>.

