	* configure.in Don't use OCTAVE_SET_DEFAULT to set values for
	bindir, datadir, exec_prefix, includedir, infodir, libdir,
	libexecdir, mandir.
	Don't use AC_PREFIX_DEFAULT, since we don't want to override the
	default setting anyway.

