	* configure.in (CXX): Export; cxxlibs.sh needs this.
	(FLIB_LIST, CXXLIB_LIST): Extract -R options along with -L options.

	* flibs.sh: Treat `-L foo' like `-Lfoo'.  Extract -R options
	like -L options.

