	* octMakefile.in (DISTDIRS): Add it

	* kpathsea: Update with 2.6 distribution.

	* Makefile.in (TARGETS): New variable.  Combine all identical targets.

	* configure.in (LIBINFO, LIBREADLINE): New variables to substitute.

